desc Box art toggle: on -> off writes fetch_covers=off, honest about kept art
config paired
seeded
settings fetch_covers=on
pick 0|Box art: All covers (on refresh)
pick 2|
expect_exit 0
expect_file_has .userdata/shared/Lodor/settings.conf fetch_covers=off
expect_trace PRES timeout=4 msg='Only downloaded games fetch box art now. Art already on the card is kept.'
